358
00:19:35,479 --> 00:19:37,880
Aku selalu menuruti perkataanmu, bukan?

359
00:19:40,019 --> 00:19:42,420
Saat kamu bersama Pak Cho tadi,

360
00:19:42,749 --> 00:19:44,789
