405
00:22:26,650 --> 00:22:28,519
"Kita akan makan apa hari ini?"

406
00:22:29,420 --> 00:22:30,450
"Deodeok?"

407
00:22:31,719 --> 00:22:32,759
"Sayang"

408
00:22:33,190 --> 00:22:34,289
"Kenapa?"

409
00:22:34,519 --> 00:22:36,160
