434
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,499
Kini kamu di rumah Han Seung Joo.

435
00:25:03,709 --> 00:25:05,180
Aku melihatmu di sana.

436
00:25:05,509 --> 00:25:06,680
Di mana kamu sekarang?

437
00:25:06,910 --> 00:25:08,110
Tunjukkan dirimu sekarang.

438
00:25:17,450 --> 00:25:18,459
